    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It requires significant mechanical attention and bodywork to be roadworthy again. The exterior has heavy rust, major paint failure, and several dents, while the interior shows substantial wear and tear. This is a dedicated project car for someone with the tools and time to perform a full restoration or for use as a parts donor.",
