    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated hobbyist looking for a project or a source for spare parts. The engine is currently very difficult to start and exhibits significant performance issues, likely requiring a full overhaul. The exterior shows heavy wear with deep scratches, several large dents, and noticeable rust patches on the body panels. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn and requires complete restoration. While the car is mostly complete, it is not currently roadworthy and will need to be towed.",
      "price": 5000.0,
